    "7224802": {
        "Desc": "Activate the spirit's trial",
        "Tips": "The Shades of Tokoyo only show up during Evernight.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Ah, if only Byakuyakoku had such valiant warriors as you! Then..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "*sigh* If this thing is done, then my wishes shall be fulfilled."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "You must bring these offerings bearing my thoughts to be enshrined... in the place where I was held under arrest. We must do this, in order to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "In order to what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "In order to... In order to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, there's no use talking to this guy now. Seems like his spirit's all messed up again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, let's just take those items with us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But where was this high-up place where this guy was imprisoned?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7224803": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Here comes one of those spirits..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "My name is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Aberaku, Helios-Forger!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "How could I have been felled by your vile slander, or imprisoned by your puppet infants!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "I— No, wait. I was imprisoned for months and years beyond count, was I not? Then... This must be my post-life form?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Post-life form\"? You mean that you're already dead, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Takes a pretty rare spirit to realize that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "And yet, though it shames me to say so, I know not just how I died..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "But I recall that I was imprisoned on orders from a child."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "A child?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Indeed. But till today, I can never feel any hatred for that child, only pity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "He was not at fault. The blame should fall upon those who controlled him like a puppet in their palms... Forget it. Such things are best left unsaid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "After that, I was imprisoned..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Imprisoned in a..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "In a...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "In a very high place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "But though it was high up, it was dark, lightless, and cold as the ice itself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "...Strange. Why is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Why do I feel that a high place should have brought a person warmth and comfort?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Why... Why can't I remember any of this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are you hungry, maybe?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whenever Paimon's famished, forget thinking, she can barely even talk straight!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think that's his issue..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Come on, it's gotta be! Look at him, he can hardly speak clearly!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, it just so happens that we have some emergen—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Actually, {NICKNAME}, could you check if there's something to eat amongst the offerings?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Wait! That's it! The offerings!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What, do you wanna eat them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "No, I just remembered..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "When I died in prison, my attire and body were enshrined in various places due to my contribution in creating the Helios."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "But that also caused my spirit to be separated and rendered unable to rest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "This place should have been the resting place of my sacred crown, though it has surely decayed by now. This must surely be why my thoughts are so... stuck."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "If this persists, I doubt that even my current state can be sustained for long..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "But these offerings can be used to replace the remnants of my body and my attire in sustaining an ounce of my thoughts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "As such, please take them with you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "However, there are many perils on the enshrining path. So though it may seem rude of me, could you accept a certain test first?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Test? What test?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Please defeat the monsters hereabouts, the prison wardens of my spirit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "This matter is perilous. Tell me once you are ready, O Traveler, and we shall begin."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
