    "7224902": {
        "Desc": "Activate the spirit's trial",
        "Tips": "The Shades of Tokoyo only show up during Evernight.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "I—Incredible! You may just be able to do this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Please then, I beg you, carry these offerings... the offerings... you must..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "You must take them away to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "To..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's wrong?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh brother, his words are getting less and less clear!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Take them to the place of enshrining... enjoin the parts of my soul, in order to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hello, Mr. Spirit?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "In order to... In order to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "In order to do what again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "In order to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, this guy isn't making himself clear at all! But it seems we're supposed to take these offerings somewhere — Paimon got that much."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "These offerings have been here for so long. Who knows if there's anything edible here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Best not to eat them all the same."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "H—Hey! Paimon doesn't just eat anything, alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Well, let's take the offerings with us anyway, {NICKNAME}."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7224903": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "My name is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Aberaku, Helios-Forger!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um, what's the Helios?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is it something very impressive?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Verily! T'was I who organized the building of the Helios with the might of an entire nation behind me, that we might resist the Dragonheirs of the Depths."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "This unsurpassed deed could have been done by no other in Byakuyakoku — none save I!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh. Guess that is pretty impressive."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But why would such a great person be sealed in here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "I... I was betrayed..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "When the sky kingdom crashed into the bottomless depths, the people were scourged by dragons, and thus did I — yes, 'twas I — begin building the Helios to save us all from our fate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "But... those ravening rogues! The moment their lives were no longer in danger, they began to deceive and lie. They even advocated placing mere infants on the throne. Laughable!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "Even I became the target of their schemes, and was left in jail to rot!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "A pox! A pox upon them all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "...Right. You."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yup, that's you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon, I think he's talking to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Nah, he's clearly looking at you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(With a very heated look in his eyes, too.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "It can only be you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "My sacred robes were once placed here, but they have all but rotted away in the passing of years, and can no longer be relied upon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "But if you can pass the test, then I shall hand the offerings, into which I have nested my thoughts, unto you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "I pray for your... success..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aberaku",
                    "T": "This matter is perilous. Tell me once you are ready, O Traveler, and we shall begin."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
